    • Constructor Detail

      • SplitHistoryEntry

        public SplitHistoryEntry(int index,
                 int numSiblings)
        Creates a new SplitHistoryEntry.
        Parameters:
        index - split index. The first split result has index 0, the second has index 1 ... the last split result has index numSiblings - 1.
        numSiblings - number of siblings. This represents the number of messages split from a (parent) message.

      • SplitHistoryEntry

        public SplitHistoryEntry(int index,
                 boolean last)
        Creates a new SplitHistoryEntry.
        Parameters:
        index - split index. The first split result has index 0, the second has index 1 ...
        last - last in result list. true if the entry is the last in the split result list.
